summary: Little mod share dogs in skyrim on male and female.
descriptionHtml:
Hi all.

This mod mod share dogs in skyrim on male and female.
This mod include dogs models with genitals, and textures. 
(It haven't got any sex animation and it won't).


See my other mod:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/60289/?


[u][b]Compatibility:
[/b][/u]It should be compatible with mods:
1. Add new dogs to skyrim. (but be shure that my mod is after them)

[u][b]No Compatibility:[/b][/u]
1. Mods who contain new meshes and textures for dogs.

[u][b]Installation:
[/b][/u]1. Download the file from nexus. ;)
2. Unpack it
3. Paste the .esp file, meshes and textures catalog to your Skyrim Data folder.

[u][b]Uninstallation:
[/b][/u]1. Delete the .esp file from your Skyrim Data folder.
2. Delete the catalog "dog" from Skyrim>Data>meshes>actors>
3. Delete the catalog "dog" from Skyrim>Data>textures>actors>
